\c 14
\s Jehovha achabata ushe hwose
\p
\v 1 Tarira, zuva raJehovha rinosvika, nenguva iyo zvawakapamba zvichagoverwa mukati mako.
\v 2 nokuti ndichaunganidza ndudzi dzose dzavanhu kuzorwa neJerusarema; guta richakundwa, dzimba dzichapambwa, navakadzi vavo vachachinyiwa; hafu yeguta vachatapwa, asi vakasara vavanhu havangabviswi muguta.
\v 3 Ipapo Jehovha achabuda, ndokurwa nendudzi idzedzo, sezvaakarwa nezuva rehondo.
\v 4 Nezuva iro tsoka dzake dzichamira pagomo reMiorivhi, riri pamberi peJerusarema kurutivi rwamabvazuva; gomo reMiorivhi richapamuka napakati, zvichibva kumabvazuva zvichienda kumavirazuva, kukavapo mupata mukuru kwazvo; imwe hafu yegomo ichatsedukira kurutivi rwokumusoro, imwe hafu yaro kurutivi rwezasi.
\v 5 Muchatiza nomumupata wamakomo angu, nokuti mupata wamakomo uchanosvika paAzeri; zvirokwazvo muchatiza, sezvamakatiza kudengenyeka kwenyika pamazuva aUziya mambo waJudha; ipapo Jehovha Mwari wenyu achauya, navatsvene vose pamwechete newe.
\p
\v 6 Zvino nezuva iro chiedza chichashaikwa, zvinopenya zvichadzimwa.
\v 7 Asi richava zuva rimwe rinozikanwa naJehovha, hapangavi namasikati kana husiku, asi nenguva yamadekwani chiedza chichavapo.
\p
\v 8 Zvino nezuva iro mvura mhenyu zhinji ichabuda muJerusarema; imwe hafu yayo ichayerera kugungwa rokumabvazuva, imwe hafu yayo kugungwa rokumavirazuva; zvichaitwa pazhizha napachando.
\v 9 Jehovha achava Mambo wenyika yose; nezuva iro Jehovha achava mumwechete, nezita rake rimwe chete.
\p
\v 10 Nyika yose ichaita sebani, zvichibva Gebha kusvikira paRimoni, kurutivi rwezasi rweJerusarema; iro richakwiridzwa, richagara panzvimbo yaro, kubva pasuwo raBhenjamini kusvikira kunzvimbo yesuwo rokutanga, kusvikira kusuwo rekona, nokubva kurutura rwaHananeri kusvikira kuzvishiro zvewaini zvamambo.
\v 11 Vanhu vachagaramo; kutukwa hakungazovipo, asi Jerusarema richagara rakachengetwa.
\p
\v 12 Uku ndiko kurova Jehovha kwaacharova nako ndudzi dzose dzavanhu vakarwa neJerusarema, nyama yavo ichaora vamire namakumbo avo, meso avo achaorera mumakomba awo, norurimi rwavo ruchaorera mumiromo yavo.
\p
\v 13 Zvino nezuva iro kunyonganiswa kukuru kunobva kuna Jehovha kuchavapo pakati pavo; umwe  neumwe   achabata ruoko rwowokwake, uye ruoko rwake ruchasimudzirwa ruoko rwowokwake.
\v 14 Judha vacharwawo paJerusarema; fuma yendudzi dzose dzavanhu vakapoteredza ichaunganidzwa, inoti ndarama, nesirivha, nenguvo, zvizhinji kwazvo.
\v 15 Sezvakaita kurohwa uku, ndizvo zvichaitawo kurohwa kwamabhiza namahesera, nengamera, nembongoro, nezvipfuwo zvose zvichavapo pamisasa iyo.
\p
\v 16 Zvino vose vakasara vendudzi dzose dzakarwa neJerusarema, vachakwira gore rimwe nerimwe kundonamata Mambo, iye Jehovha wehondo, nokutamba mutambo wamatumba.
\v 17 Ani nani pamarudzi enyika asingakwiri Jerusarema kundonamata Mambo, Jehovha wehondo, haanganisirwi mvura.
\v 18 Kana rudzi rwavaEgipita rusingakwiri, vakasasvikapo, naivo vachavingwa nokurohwa Jehovha kwaacharova nako ndudzi dzavanhu dzinoramba kukwira kundotamba mutambo wamatumba.
\v 19 Uku ndiko kurohwa kwechivi cheEgipita nokurohwa kwechivi chendudzi dzose dzinoramba kukwira kundotamba mutambo wamatumba.
\p
\v 20 Nezuva iro pamatare anorira amabhiza pachanyorwa, pachiti, ZVITSVENE KUNA JEHOVHA; nehari dziri mumba maJehovha dzichafanana nembiya dziri pamberi pearitari.
\v 21 Zvirokwazvo, hari imwe neimwe paJerusarema napaJudha ichava tsvene kuna Jehovha wehondo; vose vanoda kubayira vachauya vachidzitora, kuzobikiramo; nezuva iro hapachazovi nomuKenani mumba maJehovha wehondo.
